Package: vascr
Type: Package
Title: Toolkit for Processing Vascular Impedance Data
Version: 0.3.900
Author: person("James", "Hucklesby", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1591-6823"), role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: James Hucklesby <jhuc964@aucklanduni.ac.nz>
Description: Allows for the analyasis of ECIS, xcelligence and cellZScope data using the R enviroment. Includes tools for importing both the raw ECIS data in resampled form and modeled data generated by the ECIS package. Also includes some ggplot2 templates that allow for rapid generation of commonly used plots.
